# 构建产物（仅根目录，勿用 [Bb]uild/ 以免吞掉 third_party/webview2/build/ 里的 SDK 头）
# Build output — root only; a bare build/ glob would swallow the vendored WebView2 SDK headers.
/build/
/out/

# CMake 中间文件 / CMake intermediates
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
*.cmake.state

# Visual Studio / VS Code 本地配置 / Editor & IDE local files
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.docstates

# 系统垃圾 / OS junk
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
